description: Hike from just past Austin Pass to Lake Ann, near the base of Mount Shuksan and the Curtis Glacier. You descend around 250 m at the beginning of the trail and gain around 250-300 m towards the lake.
directions: Head East on Highway 542 (Mt Baker Highway). Follow it past the ski hill parking lot and just past Austin Pass to the parking lot and trailhead on the left (East) side of the road.
title: Lake Ann
